
      ----- NOVERIA -----

This will be my Main project in Helio-Training, the name of this project is "NOVERIA"
This project will be a online store for Movies and VideoGames 

You can see the progress of this site at: URL.....



 -- some features are: --
See individual products.
Search Movies and games in database.
Add Movies & Games to database
Ability to use a USB Bar-Code Scanner 
Sales, inventory, P&L , Balance Sheet Reports
Individual Log-In access to site.




 -- Technologies that will be used: --
Node.js
Express.js
EJS
EJS-Mate
MongoDB
Morgan
Bcrypt
Bootstrap





 -- Other features to be add in the future: --
Chat-bot to interact with customers.
Payroll for employees
Accounting sistem, for Acc. Payable & Acc. Receivable


